# Manifest — SEO fixes (2026-07-17)

Most of the originally planned changes (robots.txt, sitemap.xml, metadataBase,
title template, Open Graph/Twitter cards, product JSON-LD, canonicals on shop
and product pages, noindex on cart/checkout) already landed upstream in a
parallel redesign and were kept as-is. This commit adds only the remaining gaps:

## Modified files
src/app/admin/layout.tsx    robots noindex, nofollow meta on the whole admin panel (belt on top of the robots.txt disallow)
src/app/page.tsx            canonical "/" on the home page (only indexable page that lacked one)
CHANGES.mf                  this manifest

## Deployment note
Canonical/sitemap URLs derive from SITE_URL (src/lib/site.ts): SITE_URL env
var > Vercel production URL > localhost. Set SITE_URL once a custom domain exists.
